Runnable — simple transmit

Protocol:

inline [protocol] .uart8n1:

tx:
0
data 8b
1

:

UART:

comp [uart] .uart0:
baud: 9600
protocol: .uart8n1
:

Transmit:

.uart0:{
send = ^41
set = 1
}

Transmits:

A

