Runnable — two UARTs

Protocol:

inline [protocol] .uart8n1:

tx:
0
data 8b
1

:

Devices:

comp [uart] .a:
baud: 9600
protocol: .uart8n1
:

comp [uart] .b:
baud: 9600
protocol: .uart8n1
:

Connection:

.a:tx = .b:rx
.b:tx = .a:rx

Transmit:

.a:{
send = ^41
set = 1
}

Receive:

8wire data =
.b:data

1bit ready =
.b:dataReady

Result:

data = ^41

