Runnable — UART to Terminal

Protocol:

inline [protocol] .uart8n1:

tx:
0
data 8b
1

:

UART:

comp [uart] .uart0:
baud: 9600
protocol: .uart8n1
:

Terminal:

comp [terminal] .console:
rows: 10
columns: 40
:

Display received characters:

.console:{
append = .uart0:data
set = .uart0:dataReady
}

Every received byte is appended to the terminal.

